1 Introduction

The data we analyzed in order to define best options in terms of customer segments for DeepMetrica, is exported with the help of alexa.com. The data basically says HOW MANY WEBSITES THERE ARE IN THESE CATEGORIES. These websites are classified through main and sub-categories and is tried to find chart-toppers. Finally, the visitor numbers and traffic of websites are obtained with the help of similarweb.com.

2 Main Categories

When we look main website categories, we see that Business, Society, and Arts tagged websites constituted the biggest parts in term of numbers. At first glance, it comes to mind the websites like:

4 Conclusion

We have classified Main and Sub-Categories of the websites in which data exported from the Alexa. The barcharts showing categories which are powerful in term of weight are made. Example websites which have possibility to be our future customers are given based on those weights. In a statistical and overall view, it can be concluded that the most weighted categories are EDUCATION, BUSINESS SERVICES, and ARTS&ENTERTAINMENT with 20569, 13315, 12231 respectively.
